caption.title: List of protein expression from plasma assay library.
caption.p: The table includes the following columns: protein identifier based on the transcriptome previously published [ 35], peptide sequence identified, the precursor charge, the fragment ion, product charge, the condition (time point studied), bioreplicate (biological replicate in which the peptide was identified), and area (intensity measurement used for quantification purposes).
